				    (<AND <PRSO? ,REPORT-BUFFER>
					  <EQUAL? ,FEED-BUFFER ,NEWS-BUFFER>>
				     <TELL "\"">
				     <ERR "" T>
				     <TELL
D ,PRSO " is empty. Most recent Special Report was \"">
				     <COND (<L? ,DATE 18>
					    <TELL
"Report on America's Prison System\" on March 12.\"" CR>)
					   (T
