	 <TELL CR CR CR CR>
	 <PRINT-SPACES 22>
	 <TELL "\"A mind forever voyaging through" CR>
	 <PRINT-SPACES 23>
	 <TELL "strange seas of thought, alone.\"" CR>
	 <PRINT-SPACES 40>
	 <TELL "-- William Wordsworth" CR CR CR CR CR>
